
I like people like that. People that spread happiness without even trying. I wish I was like that.
"Well that's your own fault they're hooking up in the bathroom!" He says breathlessly after his laugh attack. "Oh hey, I can give you a ride after school if you want."
I try to get back to normal. I laughed so hard I thought I was going to get abs. It hurt to breathe now. "Sure. As long as you don't try anything on me like last time," I squinted my eyes, pointing my finger at him trying to make myself scary but still slightly laughing.
"Promise," He smiled while pushing my pointy finger down from his face slowly.